race.comment: VODKA SUNRISE (8) trailed the lead and fought on well to be beaten one length into third (17.12) at Murray Bridge Straight in a TG1-4W over 300m. Makes plenty of appeal. DEL MAR BEEPER (2) missed the frame latest (22.49) when fifth over 375m at this track in a Grade 5. Has two wins already from this draw. Can feature with the right run. VISION (1) copped a check in the run and finished a well held 12 lengths sixth (20.84) last time in a TG1-4W at Angle Park over 342m. Key player if finds best. POSSIBLE (5) among the chances again based on last run here.
